    <item>
      <title>BE表示，中国科技行业的增长动力可能与房地产相媲美</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/china-s-tech-sector-may-rival-property-as-growth-driver-be-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博经济研究称，中国的高科技行业正在推动世界第二大经济体对商品和服务的需求不断增长，其贡献可能到 2026 年可与房地产相媲美。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/china-s-tech-sector-may-rival-property-as-growth-driver-be-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:54:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对苹果、谷歌、Meta 进行新数字法测试调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟对苹果公司、Alphabet公司旗下谷歌和Meta Platforms公司是否遵守限制大型科技公司权力的严格新法律展开全面调查，它们面临着潜在巨额罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
