      <title>法院暂停之前在西班牙屏蔽 Telegram 的命令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/telegram-to-be-blocked-in-spain-on-court-order-in-content-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙一家法院暂停了早些时候发布的一项命令，该命令旨在阻止该国的即时通讯服务 Telegram，作为对非法共享电视和视频内容的用户进行调查的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/telegram-to-be-blocked-in-spain-on-court-order-in-content-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:20:22 GMT</pubDate>
